casebody.data:
Grossman v. Supreme Lodge Knights and Ladies of Honor. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 24, 1889.) For appeal from order refusing to resettle case on appeal, see-5 N. Y. Supp. 122.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

No opinion. Motion denied, with $10 costs.
